      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="name-item-bank" data-step-uuid="93ab36cd-f6ae-41cf-a794-1a2d50849267">
    <h2 id="name-item-bank" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Name Item Bank</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/806/856/original/fe905a39-8167-40d8-8553-ff0ad25c84de.png" srcset="" alt="Name Item Bank" height="332" width="495">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_c0d6eca5-ba06-4bc3-a85b-39e6df21b5a6" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the <strong>Bank Name</strong> field [1], enter the name of the item bank. You can share the new item bank to the current course by clicking the <strong>Share </strong>checkbox [2]. To save your bank, click the <strong>Create Bank</strong> button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
