<p>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-duplicate-an-Item-Bank/ta-p/587636" target="_blank">duplicate the item bank</a>, click the <strong>Duplicate</strong> icon [2]. To share the item bank, click the <strong>Share</strong> icon [3]. To edit the item bank, click the <strong>Edit</strong> icon [4]. To delete the item bank, click the <strong>Delete</strong> icon [5].</p>
